#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:227
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api\\developer\\changelog-roadmap.md:227"
msgid "Audit log — database persistence fixes"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:229
msgid ""
"`persistAuditLog()` in `audit.service.ts` refactored to pass an explicit "
"named-parameter object to pg-promise instead of spreading `AuditLogEntry`. "
"The spread caused pg-promise to throw `Property 'resourceType' doesn't "
"exist` for any field not referenced in the SQL template (specifically `azp` "
"added in v2.8.1), silently suppressing all audit log writes to the database "
"on ACC."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:231
msgid ""
"`ipAddress` port stripping now applied in the explicit object — Azure App "
"Service appends the port to `req.ip`, which is invalid for PostgreSQL `inet` "
"type. This error was masked by the spread error and is now also fixed."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:235
msgid "v2.8.1 — March 19, 2026"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:237
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api\\developer\\changelog-roadmap.md:237"
msgid "Audit log — M2M tenant fallback"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:239
msgid ""
"`persistAuditLog()` now falls back to the `azp` claim when `tenantId` is "
"absent, preventing a NOT NULL violation on `tenant_id` for service account "
"tokens. The fallback is applied only at the point of DB persistence — "
"`req.user.tenantId` is unchanged."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:241
msgid ""
"`jwt.middleware.ts` reverted: `tenantId` is set exclusively from the "
"`municipality` claim. The earlier `azp` fallback on `req.user` caused "
"`tenantMiddleware` to pass M2M tokens through to tenant-scoped routes, "
"returning empty data instead of `MISSING_TENANT`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:243
msgid ""
"`azp?: string` added to `AuditLogEntry` in `audit.types.ts` and to "
"`AuthContext` in `auth.types.ts`. `azp` populated on `req.auth` in "
"`jwt.middleware.ts` and passed through `createAuditLog()` — eliminates type "
"casts in `audit.middleware.ts`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:247
msgid "v2.8.0 — March 19, 2026"
