msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:494
msgid ""
"All user tasks (`Sub_CaseReview`, `Task_Phase6_Notify`, "
"`Task_RequestMissingInfo`) now use `camunda:candidateGroups=\"caseworker\"` "
"instead of `camunda:assignee`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:495
