msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:510
msgid ""
"Added a dedicated caseworker login path to the MijnOmgeving landing page. A "
"slate-coloured \"Inloggen als Medewerker\" button, visually separated from "
"the three citizen IdP options by a \"MEDEWERKERS\" section divider, "
"initiates the new flow. `AuthCallback` uses `check-sso` instead of `login-"
"required`, so caseworkers with an active Keycloak SSO session bypass the "
"login screen on subsequent visits. When a new session is required, "
"`keycloak.login({ loginHint: '__medewerker__' })` redirects to Keycloak, "
"where the custom `login.ftl` theme detects the sentinel and renders an "
"indigo \"Inloggen als gemeentemedewerker\" context banner with \"Medewerker "
"portaal\" as the page title."
msgstr ""

