msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ccopilot-studio-edocs.md:59
msgid ""
"When `EDOCS_STUB_MODE=true` (the current default on ACC), all four endpoints "
"return realistic fake responses. No live eDOCS server is contacted. The stub "
"is fully transparent to callers — the response shape is identical to what a "
"live server returns."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ccopilot-studio-edocs.md:61
msgid ""
"This allows Copilot Studio to be connected and tested end-to-end before live "
"DOCUVITT credentials are available."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ccopilot-studio-edocs.md:63
