#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ccopilot-studio-edocs.md:79
msgid ""
"!!! warning \"Rotate the client secret before switching to live mode\" The "
"`copilot-studio-edocs` Keycloak client secret currently used on ACC is "
"acceptable while the stub is active — it provides access only to fake data. "
"As soon as `EDOCS_STUB_MODE=false` is set and real DOCUVITT credentials are "
"configured, generate a new client secret in the Keycloak admin console and "
"update the Copilot Studio connector accordingly."
