msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ccopilot-studio-edocs.md:174
msgid ""
"The service implementation was verified against the **eDOCS REST API "
