msgid "Why the split?"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Coverview.md:63
msgid ""
"**VM (full control):**\n"
"Keycloak requires deep customisation for government compliance (DigiD "
"federation, custom JWT mappers, realm import). Operaton is a frequently "
"updated open-source engine where container control simplifies upgrades. Both "
"run in Docker on a VM at approximately €30/month total."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Coverview.md:66
msgid ""
"**Azure (managed services):**\n"
"The stateless frontend and backend benefit from auto-scaling, managed TLS, "
"deployment slots, and built-in monitoring. Azure Static Web Apps provides a "
"CDN for the frontend at negligible cost."
msgstr ""

