msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend-development.md:392
msgid ""
"The CSS import is required — without it the form renders completely unstyled."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend-development.md:394
msgid "Callback stability pattern"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend-development.md:396
msgid ""
"All three form components store callbacks (`onCompleted`, `onStarted`, "
"`onError`) in refs rather than including them in the `useEffect` dependency "
"array. Without this, inline arrow functions passed from a parent cause the "
"effect to re-fire on every render, instantiating a new `Form` object and "
"looping indefinitely."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend-development.md:398
msgid ""
"const onStartedRef = useRef(onStarted);\n"
"const onErrorRef = useRef(onError);\n"
"\n"
"useEffect(() => { onStartedRef.current = onStarted; }, [onStarted]);\n"
"useEffect(() => { onErrorRef.current = onError; }, [onError]);\n"
"\n"
"// Main init effect — callbacks intentionally NOT in the dependency array:\n"
"useEffect(() => { /* importSchema, attach listeners */ }, [processKey]);"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend-development.md:409
msgid "Container div must always be in the DOM"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend-development.md:411
msgid ""
"The `<div ref={containerRef} />` must be present in the DOM **before** "
"`form.importSchema` is called. Conditional rendering (`status === 'loading' "
"&& <div ref={...} />`) means `containerRef.current` is `null` when the "
"effect fires. Always render the container div and toggle visibility via a "
"CSS class:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend-development.md:413
msgid ""
"<div ref={containerRef} className={status === 'ready' ? 'fjs-container' : "
"'hidden'} />"
msgstr ""

