"\n"
"# IOU GitLab Integration\n"
"\n"
"The RONL Business API includes a lightweight proxy to the IOU Architecture "
"GitLab repository (`git.open-regels.nl`). It is used by the IOU tab in the "
"Flevoland tenant of the caseworker dashboard to allow external contributors "
"to submit use-case scenarios, provide feedback, and browse submitted work "
"items — without requiring a GitLab account.\n"
"\n"
"---\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

