#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ciou-gitlab-integration.md:68
msgid ""
"Uploads a single file of any type to the GitLab project uploads API and "
"returns the GitLab Markdown reference. Used by `IouGebruiksscenarioSection` "
"to pre-upload attachments before the use-case JSON body is submitted, so "
"that the file markdown references can be embedded in the issue description."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ciou-gitlab-integration.md:70
msgid "**Form field:** `file` (single file, any MIME type, up to 10 MB)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ciou-gitlab-integration.md:72
msgid ""
"**Response:** `201 { success: true, data: { markdown: \"![filename](upload-"
"url)\" } }`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ciou-gitlab-integration.md:74
msgid ""
"Uses a dedicated `uploadAny` multer instance without the image-only "
"`fileFilter` applied to the `/feedback` route. No authentication required."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ciou-gitlab-integration.md:76
msgid ""
"!!! note \"Why separate from `/use-case`\" The `/use-case` route accepts "
"`Content-Type: application/json`. Combining file uploads with text fields in "
"a single `multipart/form-data` request caused multer v2 to silently discard "
"all text fields (`req.body` was empty regardless of field presence). Pre-"
"uploading via `/upload-file` and embedding the returned references in the "
"JSON body avoids this."
msgstr ""

