msgid "LLM Provider Architecture"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cllm-provider-architecture.md:3
msgid ""
"The AI Assistant decouples the agentic loop from any specific LLM SDK "
"through a `LlmProvider` interface and a `LlmRegistry` singleton. Adding a "
"new LLM (Mistral, Azure OpenAI, Google Gemini, etc.) requires only "
"implementing the interface and registering the provider at startup — no "
"changes to the chat service, routes, or frontend are needed."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cllm-provider-architecture.md:5
msgid ""
"See [MCP AI Assistant]{1} for the overall architecture and MCP source "
"registry."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cllm-provider-architecture.md:9
msgid "Interface"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cllm-provider-architecture.md:11
msgid ""
"`packages/backend/src/services/llm/LlmProvider.ts` defines the contract "
"every provider must satisfy."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cllm-provider-architecture.md:12
msgid ""
"export interface LlmProvider {\n"
"  readonly meta: LlmProviderMeta;\n"
"  isAvailable(): boolean;\n"
"  streamTurn(\n"
"    params: LlmStreamParams,\n"
"    onDelta: (text: string) => void,\n"
"    signal?: AbortSignal\n"
"  ): Promise<LlmTurnResult>;\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cllm-provider-architecture.md:24
msgid ""
"`isAvailable()` returns `false` when the provider's API key is not "
"configured. Unavailable providers are registered but their models are "
"excluded from `GET /v1/mcp/models`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cllm-provider-architecture.md:26
msgid ""
"`streamTurn()` receives a provider-agnostic `AgentMessage[]` history, a "
"system prompt, and tool definitions. It calls `onDelta` for each text chunk "
"and returns an `LlmTurnResult` containing the full response text, any tool "
"use blocks, and the stop reason. The chat service (`mcpChat.service.ts`) "
"never imports any SDK directly."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cllm-provider-architecture.md:28
