#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:41
msgid ""
"The `OperatonMcpProvider` spawns the `operaton-mcp` npm package as a stdio "
"child process and allows the following 16 tools:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:43
msgid ""
