msgid "System prompt conventions"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:200
msgid ""
"The system prompt instructs Claude to use `maxResults=20` when listing "
"resources for display, use dedicated count tools when counting, filter by "
"`latestVersion=true` for process definitions and decisions unless the user "
"asks for version history, and never narrate tool calls in the response text "
"— only return the final answer."
msgstr ""

