"separate assistant bubble renders below the confirmed message history. It "
"displays `streamingContent` with a blinking cursor (`animate-pulse`). When "
"`done` arrives, the accumulated text is committed to the `messages` array "
"via `onMessagesChange` and the streaming state is cleared."
