#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:1
msgid "API Design"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:3
msgid ""
"RONL Business API follows the **Dutch Government API Design Rules** "
"(Nederlandse API Strategie). The API is versioned, uses standard HTTP "
"semantics, and provides machine-readable metadata via response headers."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:7
msgid "Versioning"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:9
msgid ""
"All current endpoints are served under the `/v1/` prefix (rule API-20: major "
"version in the URI path). A response header `API-Version` is added to every "
"response (rule API-57):"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:11
msgid ""
"HTTP/1.1 200 OK\n"
"API-Version: 1.0.0\n"
"Content-Type: application/json"
msgstr ""

