"inspecting running processes, viewing audit history, and managing "
"deployments."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:1
msgid "Caseworker Dashboard"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:3
msgid ""
"The MijnOmgeving caseworker dashboard is the primary interface for "
"municipality staff. It is a shell-based single-page application that loads "
"at `/dashboard/caseworker` and remains publicly accessible — authentication "
"is handled inside the component rather than at the route level, allowing "
"unauthenticated visitors to browse public content before logging in."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:12
msgid "Shell layout"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:14
msgid "The dashboard is divided into three permanent zones:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:16
msgid ""
"┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n"
"│  Top navigation bar (header)                                        │\n"
"│  MijnOmgeving  [Home] [Persoonlijke info] [Projecten]               │\n"
"│                [Gereedschap] [Audit log]                      User  │\n"
"├──────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n"
"│ Left panel   │                                                      │\n"
"│ (w-56)       │  Main content area                                   │\n"
"│              │                                                      │\n"
"│ Section nav  │  Rendered by renderContent()                         │\n"
"│              │  based on activeSection                              │\n"
"└──────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:30
msgid ""
"!!! note \"Tenant vs Platform\" Tenant-configured pages (Home, Persoonlijke "
"info, Projecten) are driven by `tenants.json`. Platform-scoped pages "
"(Gereedschap, Audit log) are hardcoded in `CaseworkerDashboard.tsx` — they "
"always appear for authenticated users regardless of tenant."
