#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:52
msgid "BPMN linking"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:54
msgid ""
"Forms are linked to BPMN elements using the `camunda:formRef` and "
"`camunda:formRefBinding` attributes:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:56
msgid ""
"<bpmn:startEvent id=\"StartEvent_1\">\n"
"  <bpmn:extensionElements>\n"
"    <camunda:formData>\n"
"      <camunda:formRef>kapvergunning-start</camunda:formRef>\n"
"      <camunda:formRefBinding>latest</camunda:formRefBinding>\n"
"    </camunda:formData>\n"
"  </bpmn:extensionElements>\n"
"</bpmn:startEvent>"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:67
msgid ""
"`camunda:formRefBinding=\"latest\"` instructs Operaton to always resolve the "
"most recently deployed version of the form ID — no version pinning required. "
"The LDE BPMN Modeler writes these attributes automatically via the **Link to "
"Form** dropdown."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:71
msgid "Deployment"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:73
msgid ""
"Forms must be deployed to Operaton alongside the BPMN in the same deployment "
"bundle so that `camunda:formRef` can resolve at runtime (all resources share "
"one deployment ID). The [LDE BPMN Modeler one-click deploy]{1} bundles the "
"main BPMN, any referenced subprocess BPMNs, and all linked `.form` files "
"automatically."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:77
msgid "Runtime rendering"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:79
msgid "Citizen start form — `ProcessStartFormViewer`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:81
msgid ""
"When the citizen opens the Kapvergunning service, `ProcessStartFormViewer` "
"calls `GET /v1/process/AwbShellProcess/start-form` to fetch the deployed "
"schema. `@bpmn-io/form-js` renders the form with `applicantId` and "
"`productType` as hidden initial data. On submit, the form variables are "
"forwarded directly to `POST /v1/process/AwbShellProcess/start`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:83
msgid ""
"If no form has been deployed, the portal shows \"Geen formulier "
"beschikbaar\" and the service cannot be started."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:85
msgid "Caseworker task forms — `TaskFormViewer`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:87
msgid ""
"After claiming a task, `TaskFormViewer` calls `GET /v1/task/:id/form-"
"schema`. The task's current process variables are pre-populated as initial "
"data so the caseworker sees the latest DMN outcomes immediately. On submit, "
"the form data completes the task via `POST /v1/task/:id/complete`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:89
msgid "Tasks without a deployed form fall back to a generic complete button."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:91
msgid "Decision Viewer — `DecisionViewer`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:93
msgid ""
"Completed applications in **Mijn aanvragen** show a **Bekijk beslissing** "
"toggle. Clicking it expands the Decision Viewer panel beneath the "
"application card."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:95
msgid "On mount, `DecisionViewer` fires two requests in parallel:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:97
msgid ""
"`GET /v1/process/:id/historic-variables` — retrieves the final variable "
"state from the Operaton history API. The backend flattens the historic "
"variable instances and applies tenant isolation via the `municipality` "
"variable."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:98
msgid ""
"`GET /v1/process/:id/decision-document` — resolves the `DocumentTemplate` "
"bundled in the Operaton deployment. The backend reads the `ronl:documentRef` "
"attribute from the BPMN UserTask XML, then fetches the corresponding "
"`.document` resource from the deployment bundle."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:100
msgid ""
"**Document template path (v2.3.0+):** If the document endpoint returns a "
"template, `DecisionViewer` renders it as styled HTML. TipTap/ProseMirror "
"JSON `text` blocks are rendered as React elements — bold, italic, and "
"underline marks are preserved. `{{variableKey}}` placeholders in text blocks "
"are substituted with the resolved historic process variables. `variable` "
"blocks render the value directly by key. The letterhead and contact "
"information zones are displayed side-by-side in a CSS grid, matching the "
"Document Composer canvas layout."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:107
msgid ""
"**Form-js fallback path (pre-v2.3.0 deployments):** If `GET /v1/process/:id/"
"decision-document` returns 404 `DOCUMENT_NOT_FOUND` (no `ronl:documentRef` "
"present, or the `.document` resource is absent from the deployment bundle), "
"`DecisionViewer` falls back to rendering a hardcoded readonly `@bpmn-io/form-"
"js` schema with five fields: `status`, `permitDecision`, `finalMessage`, "
"`replacementInfo`, and `dossierReference`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cdynamic-forms.md:109
msgid "Caseworker-only action fields are excluded from both rendering paths."
msgstr ""

