msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cprocesbibliotheek.md:25
msgid "`bpmnProcessId` (the Operaton process definition key)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cprocesbibliotheek.md:26
msgid "Status badge: **WIP**, **Actief**, or **Concept**"
