msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Cstandards-compliance.md:7
msgid ""
"Overall information security baseline. RONL implements BIO controls "
"including access management (Keycloak RBAC), audit logging (PostgreSQL), and "
"secure transmission (TLS everywhere)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Cstandards-compliance.md:7
