#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Cadding-municipality.md:1
msgid "Adding a Municipality"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Cadding-municipality.md:3
msgid ""
"This guide is for system operators and developers onboarding a new Dutch "
"municipality to RONL Business API. Three things need to be configured: the "
"tenant configuration file, Keycloak users and groups, and (optionally) "
"municipality-specific feature flags."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Cadding-municipality.md:7
msgid "1. Add the tenant configuration"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Cadding-municipality.md:9
msgid ""
"Edit `packages/frontend/public/tenants.json` and add an entry for the new "
"municipality. Use the following structure:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Cadding-municipality.md:11
msgid ""
"{\n"
"  \"tenants\": {\n"
"    \"newtown\": {\n"
"      \"id\": \"newtown\",\n"
"      \"name\": \"newtown\",\n"
"      \"displayName\": \"Gemeente Nieuwstad\",\n"
"      \"municipalityCode\": \"0999\",\n"
"      \"theme\": {\n"
"        \"primary\": \"#2E4057\",\n"
"        \"primaryDark\": \"#1A2A3A\",\n"
"        \"primaryLight\": \"#6B8CAD\",\n"
"        \"secondary\": \"#F4A261\",\n"
"        \"accent\": \"#E76F51\"\n"
"      },\n"
"      \"features\": {\n"
"        \"zorgtoeslag\": true,\n"
"        \"kinderbijslag\": false,\n"
"        \"huurtoeslag\": false,\n"
"        \"processes\": [\"zorgtoeslag\"]\n"
"      },\n"
"      \"contact\": {\n"
"        \"phone\": \"14 0999\",\n"
"        \"email\": \"info@nieuwstad.nl\",\n"
"        \"address\": \"Stadhuis 1\",\n"
"        \"postalCode\": \"1234 AB\",\n"
"        \"city\": \"Nieuwstad\"\n"
"      },\n"
"      \"enabled\": true\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Cadding-municipality.md:45
msgid ""
"The `id` value must match the `municipality` claim that Keycloak will issue "
"in the JWT for users of this municipality (see step 2 below)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Cadding-municipality.md:47
msgid ""
"Theme colours follow the municipality's visual identity. The `primary` "
"colour is applied to buttons, headers, and active navigation items. Use "
"sufficient contrast against white text (WCAG AA minimum)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Cadding-municipality.md:51
msgid "2. Configure Keycloak"
msgstr ""

