#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:124
msgid "Step 1 — Visit the portal and select \"Inloggen als Medewerker\""
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:126
msgid ""
"On the MijnOmgeving landing page, scroll past the three citizen options. "
"Below a \"MEDEWERKERS\" divider you will find the slate-coloured caseworker "
"button."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:133
msgid "Step 2 — AuthCallback checks for an existing SSO session"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:135
msgid ""
"Clicking \"Inloggen als Medewerker\" stores `medewerker` in `sessionStorage` "
"and navigates to `/auth`. `AuthCallback.tsx` detects this and calls:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:137
msgid ""
"keycloak.init({\n"
"  onLoad: 'check-sso',\n"
"  checkLoginIframe: false,\n"
"});"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:144
msgid ""
"Unlike the citizen flow (`login-required`), `check-sso` does **not** trigger "
"a redirect. It silently checks whether a Keycloak SSO session already exists "
"in the browser:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:146
msgid ""
"**Session found** → navigates directly to `/dashboard` without any login "
"screen."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:147
msgid "**No session** → proceeds to step 3."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:149
msgid "Step 3 — Keycloak login with caseworker banner"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:151
msgid "When no SSO session exists, `AuthCallback` calls:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:153
msgid "keycloak.login({ loginHint: '__medewerker__' });"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:157
msgid ""
"This redirects to Keycloak and passes `__medewerker__` as the `login_hint` "
"parameter. The `login.ftl` FreeMarker template reads this value via "
"`login.username`, detects the sentinel string `__medewerker__`, and:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:159
msgid ""
"Sets the page title to **\"Medewerker portaal\"** instead of the default "
"\"Inloggen\""
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:160
msgid "Renders an indigo context banner: **\"Inloggen als medewerker\"**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:161
msgid ""
"Suppresses the sentinel value from the username field (the field renders "
"empty, so the caseworker types their own username)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:168
msgid "Step 4 — Enter credentials"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:170
msgid ""
"Enter the Keycloak username and password for the caseworker account. Click "
"**Inloggen**."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:172
msgid ""
"A \"← Terug naar inlogkeuze\" link is available below the login button to "
"return to the landing page without completing login."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:174
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api\\user-guide\\login-flow.md:174"
msgid "Step 5 — Token issuance"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:176
msgid ""
"Keycloak issues a JWT with `roles: [\"caseworker\"]` and the caseworker's "
"`municipality` attribute."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:178
msgid "**Example JWT payload (caseworker):**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:180
msgid ""
"{\n"
"  \"sub\": \"xyz789abc012\",\n"
"  \"name\": \"Petra van Dam\",\n"
"  \"preferred_username\": \"test-caseworker-utrecht\",\n"
"  \"municipality\": \"utrecht\",\n"
"  \"loa\": \"hoog\",\n"
"  \"realm_access\": {\n"
"    \"roles\": [\"caseworker\"]\n"
"  },\n"
"  \"aud\": \"ronl-business-api\",\n"
"  \"iss\": \"https://acc.keycloak.open-regels.nl/realms/ronl\",\n"
"  \"exp\": 1708534800,\n"
"  \"iat\": 1708533900\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:197
msgid "Step 6 — Caseworker dashboard"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:199
msgid ""
"The portal detects the `caseworker` role in the JWT and renders the "
"caseworker dashboard. See [Caseworker Workflow]{1} for what caseworkers can "
"do once logged in."
msgstr ""

