#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:1
msgid "Submitting an Application"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:3
msgid ""
"This guide covers the **Kapvergunning** (tree felling permit) application — "
"the AWB process currently available in the RONL Business API citizen portal. "
"For the zorgtoeslag calculator and application, see [Applying for "
"Zorgtoeslag via Unive]{1}."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:7
msgid "Kapvergunning (tree felling permit application)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:9
msgid ""
"The tree felling permit is an **asynchronous, multi-actor process** "
"implementing the Dutch Administrative Law Act (Awb). Unlike a simple "
"calculation, the citizen submits an application and receives a dossier "
"reference — the actual decision is made later by a caseworker and "
"communicated separately."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:16
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api\\user-guide\\submitting-application.md:16"
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:18
msgid ""
"You must be logged in with DigiD assurance level **midden** or higher. See "
"[Logging In — Citizen & Caseworker]{1}."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:20
msgid "Submitting the application"
msgstr ""

