msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:24
msgid ""
"After login, select **Vergunningen** from the services catalogue, then "
"choose **Kapvergunning aanvragen**."
msgstr ""

