#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:153
msgid ""
"!!! note \"Caseworker override\" The caseworker can override the DMN outcome "
"during `Sub_CaseReview` by selecting **Wijzigen** and choosing a different "
"permit decision. The override is stored in `reviewAction = change` alongside "
"`reviewPermitDecision`. Both the original DMN result and the caseworker "
"override are preserved in the process variables for audit purposes."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:158
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api\\user-guide\\submitting-application.md:158"
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:160
msgid ""
"**Form submits but no result appears** Check that the API Health indicator "
"in the portal header shows all services as UP. If Operaton shows \"down\", "
"the business rules engine is temporarily unavailable."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:163
msgid ""
"**500 error on submission** The most common cause is a double-wrapped "
"variable format in the tenant middleware. Check the backend log for `Must "
"provide 'null' or String value for value of SerializableValue type 'Json'`. "
"See [Troubleshooting]{1}."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:166
msgid ""
"**Error: FORBIDDEN / LOA_INSUFFICIENT** Your DigiD assurance level is too "
"low for this service. Log out and log in again using DigiD with SMS code "
"(midden) or the ID check app (hoog)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:169
msgid ""
"**Error: RATE_LIMIT_EXCEEDED** Too many requests from your session. Wait one "
"minute and try again."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Csubmitting-application.md:172
msgid ""
"**Task not visible in caseworker queue** The task queue filters by "
"`municipality` process variable. Verify that the citizen and caseworker "
"accounts belong to the same municipality in Keycloak. See [Caseworker "
"Workflow]{1}."
msgstr ""

